# Task: Predict Future Stock Prices (Short-Term)

This project is part of the AI/ML Engineering Internship at DevelopersHub.

## 🔍 Objective
Use historical stock data to predict the next day's closing price using regression models.

## 📁 Files
- `Task2_Stock_Price_Prediction.ipynb`: Main notebook for data preprocessing, modeling, and visualization.
- `stock_data.csv`: Historical stock prices for 5 different stocks.
- `README.md`: This documentation.

## 🧠 Techniques Used
- Time series data handling with pandas
- Feature engineering with lag values
- Random Forest Regressor from scikit-learn
- Mean Squared Error (MSE) for evaluation
- Plotting with matplotlib

## 📊 Result
The model successfully captured stock price trends with a low Mean Squared Error.

## 📌 Notes
Data was synthetically generated and does not represent real market data.

